試寫出以下 HTML碼的顯示結果,並清楚標示CSS 屬性的影響:(5%)
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
h1 {
  color: red;
  display: none;
}
h1.h {
}
p {
  background-color: lightgrey;
  width: 300px;
  padding: 10px;
  border: 2px solid;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>This is heading1</h1>
<h1 class="h">This is heading2</h1>
<p>CSS describes how HTML elements are to be displayed on screen, paper, or in
other media.</p>
</body>
</html>
```

